./sdp/prd-snapshot.md:25:| R750-005 | Add local infinite-quota short-circuit to `quota_monitor.py` so provider `"local"` always returns 1.0 headroom and is never rate-limited. | MUST | T1 | - `get_agent_headroom("ollama")` returns 1.0<br/>- Ollama is never excluded from selection due to quota<br/>- Tests verify infinite headroom for local provider |
