./sdp/logs/Lead_T-001_20260408T223256Z_1775687592.log:1612:my-claw/sdp/prd-r750-ollama-integration.md:15:| R750-001 | Add `ollama` to the `PROVIDERS` map in `agent_selector.py` with provider type `"local"` and seed fitness scores for 9 task categories. | MUST | T1 | - `PROVIDERS["ollama"]` returns `"local"`<br/>- Default fitness scores exist for all 9 categories<br/>- `netops` category seeded highest (0.80) reflecting LG SoT use case |
